OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will see sunny
OL,6,Fspells and the chance of a few
OL,7,Fshowers. This afternoon will be bright
OL,8,Fwith a few showers at first, otherwise
OL,9,Fdry. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry and
OL,12,Fcold. Shetland will remain dry
OL,13,Fovernight but thickening cloud will
OL,14,Fbring rain to Orkney during the early
OL,15,Fhours. Freshening southeasterly winds
OL,16,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
