OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FSome rain across Shetland in
OL,6,Fthe morning. Otherwise it will be dry
OL,7,Fmainly dry and cloudy but rain likely
OL,8,Flater in the afternoon. Strong
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fon Wednesday with rain at times.
OL,13,FBreezy and somewhat brighter on
OL,14,FThursday and Friday with showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
